|Archaeopteryx owenii|Petronievics, 1917 [''nomen rejectum'']
|Jurapteryx recurva?|(Howgate, 1985) Howgate, 1984 [originally ''Archaeopteryx'']
|[[Wellnhoferia grandis]]?|El≈ºanowski, 2001}}
