   |ethnicity         = [[European American]]
   |field             = [[Educational psychology]]
   |work_institution  = Editorial boards of ''[[Intelligence (journal)|Intelligence]]'' and ''[[Personality and Individual Differences]]
   |alma_mater        = [[Columbia University]]
   |doctoral_advisor  =
