      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox Ethnic group
|group     = Aleut
|image     = [[Image:aleut.jpg|250px]]&lt;br&gt;Traditional Aleut dress
|pop       = 17,000 to 18,000
|region1   = {{flagcountry|United States}}
|pop1      = 17,000&lt;ref&gt;including 5,000 part-Aleut{{Citation needed|date=February 2007}}&lt;/ref&gt;
|ref1      =
