      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox broadcasting network|
|network_name = Australian Broadcasting Corporation (ABC)
|network_logo = [[File:Australian Broadcasting Corporation.svg|Australian Broadcasting Corporation logo|240px]]
|country      = Australia
|network_type = {{nowrap|[[Terrestrial television|Broadcast]]&lt;br /&gt;radio&lt;br /&gt;television&lt;br /&gt;[[Website|online]] and mobile }}
